19:T429,Internal brochure evidence clearly identifies this as a spinal needle product line (RI-PRICK Spinal Needles) used for spinal anesthesia in orthopedic surgeries. The product is categorized under Critical Care > Regional Anesthesia, which is consistent with spinal needle applications. Material is confirmed as surgical-grade stainless steel. External evidence sources do not provide specific verification for RI-PRICK branded products but do confirm Meril Life Sciences manufactures medical devices including needles. The entity type is 'consumable' as spinal needles are single-use disposable devices, not implants. Confidence is set at 0.85 due to complete internal documentation alignment, but review is recommended due to: (1) brand field being empty despite 'RI-PRICK' appearing consistently as the product family name, (2) lack of specific external verification for this particular product line, and (3) truncated brochure description suggesting incomplete source data. No SKU examples available for further verification. No conflicts detected between sources.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles","product_name_display":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles","sku_code":"MRL-RPK-008","product_family":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles","product_family_display":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles","slug":"ri-prick-spinal-needles","images":[{"id":"3cfaf1a24917","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3dee16be1486691088242/cc_cover_fa5ca368.jpg","original_filename":"critical_care_p0.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":228471,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:06:36.126177+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction"}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles | RI-PRICK Regional Anesthesia - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"RI-PRICK Spinal Needles are high-performance stainless steel medical devices engineered for precise spinal anesthesia procedures in orthopedic surgeries. The...","pack_size":"Single needl